message:
These statements by the defense attorney are consistent with the mindset that needs changing. 
A victim does not have to be bound by physical chains to keep them in a sex trafficking situation. It’s the mental chains that you can’t see that traffickers use that keep victims trapped. 
“No one was locked in a room. No one was smuggled across a border” argued attorney Sean Buckley. “This is not a sex trafficking case.”
https://buff.ly/2O0vKDt
